name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: New Tab To Right Keyboard Shortcut

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a keyboard shortcut for opening a new tab to right. If grouped, adds to tab group.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a keyboard shortcut for opening a new tab to right. If the current tab is part of a tab group, the new tab will be added to the same group.
